content:
The chunk pertains to the creation and configuration of a GUI tab within a particle effect factory application. Specifically, it sets up a Float entry control for adjusting the 'Final Angle Spread' parameter in one of the factory configurations and initializes an 'OrientedParticleFactory' tab as a placeholder without implementation.

'Final Angle Spread',
            'Spread of the final angle',
            fRollover = 1,
            command = self.setFactoryZSpinFinalAngleSpread)
        # Oriented page #
        orientedPage = self.factoryNotebook.add('OrientedParticleFactory')
        tk.Label(orientedPage, text = 'Not implemented').pack(expand = 1,
                                                              fill = tk.BOTH)
        self.factoryNotebook.pack(expand = 1, fill = tk.BOTH)
